	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm working on a game.  This is my checklist
<br />-hit detection between objects
<br />-enemy behavior
<br />-environment stuff
<br />-win/loss checking
<br />-sound engine
<br />-better gfx (?)
<br />
<br />What's done now
<br />-character physics
<br />-hit detection with playfield
<br />-loading/displaying room
<br />-scrolling from one room to next (This is a single-screen game)
<br />-character animation, where applicable
<br />
<br />It's been fun to work on but I'd feel more motivated with more entries.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
